Clone the repository:
Open your terminal or command prompt and run:

git clone [https://github.com/razvanberbecar/stockscreener.git](https://github.com/razvanberbecar/stockscreener.git)
cd stockscreener


Install the required libraries:
It's highly recommended to use a Python virtual environment (venv) for this.

# Create a virtual environment (optional but recommended)
python -m venv venv

# Activate it:
# On Windows:
.\venv\Scripts\activate
# On macOS/Linux:
source venv/bin/activate

# Install the libraries
pip install pandas yfinance requests lxml html5lib


Run the script:

python stock_screener.py
